{"tid":1973302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局宣布DSE如期4月24開考","createTime":"2020-04-15T06:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T06:39:50.000Z","uid":164771,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6860152195af9d21f9ea88159ab1c2b5e1463e1a","tid":1973302,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:12:37.000Z","msg":"教育局今日宣布，2020年中學文憑試筆試將於4月24日（下週五）正式開考，7月22日放榜。如有大型感染，將延期至5月22日，如不幸6月11日仍無法開考，將取消DSE，會根據校內成績評核。"},{"pid":"eebb0255a168155090bbea7eb4e02c6874b912ff","tid":1973302,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80ce8ec0f020899110284c49a9d14cc2f8f2a61","tid":1973302,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:24:29.000Z","msg":"逾九成考生反對<br />\n港共：吹咩 打我囉笨柒"},{"pid":"b295d9d8d8e6a95b7491739c9c855f73e7969680","tid":1973302,"uid":45353,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:26:13.000Z","msg":"回力鏢開始~"},{"pid":"d90769019a05d5acc7a94aa3bfc930a64a0db525","tid":1973302,"uid":183576,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:28:29.000Z","msg":"有冇汁汁"},{"pid":"a7d52eb3866000ed692bae83596fbaa84da1f85f","tid":1973302,"uid":186072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:32:01.000Z","msg":"究竟政府諗緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇諗過考緊期間會有仆街玩野狂咳<br />\n現場監考既可以點？<br />\n請佢走？捉佢走？"},{"pid":"7f1b5d82cf4922c67a5e21c08d77d983a2b20c72","tid":1973302,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:34:50.000Z","msg":"其實呢，少一年本地year 1學生，大學真係會收皮？"},{"pid":"451f56fbd0069b707549a36446759ac5430cf4ac","tid":1973302,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:36:33.000Z","msg":"你延期都可以，只係呢年新生會無左假期咁解，點解呢個政府會咁on9"},{"pid":"7020a6190d8184b7d7c76fc4de462e2f9e698405","tid":1973302,"uid":164771,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d90769019a05d5acc7a94aa3bfc930a64a0db525","tid":1973302,"uid":183576,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:28:29.000Z","msg":"有冇汁汁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:37:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200415/RME6WH6G2V667DWO7Q6FBFPD4E/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2K_6a-O_HVFCahmUts4lqbeMOPSsAthQJfWSijtdu59dtIFSfZCRXUkuY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200415%2FRME6WH6G2V667DWO7Q6FBFPD4E%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2K_6a-O_HVFCahmUts4lqbeMOPSsAthQJfWSijtdu59dtIFSfZCRXUkuY&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQDcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=ca7ae063\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200415%2FRME6WH6G2V667DWO7Q6FBFPD4E%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2K_6a-O_HVFCahmUts4lqbeMOPSsAthQJfWSijtdu59dtIFSfZCRXUkuY&h=821edc69\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200415/RME6WH6G2V667DWO7Q6FBFPD4E/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2K_6a-O_HVFCahmUts4lqbeMOPSsAthQJfWSijtdu59dtIFSfZCRXUkuY</a><br />\n<br />\n本港武漢肺炎確診數字近日增幅有所緩和，專家雖告誡仍要保持社交距離，但特首林鄭月娥昨（14日）明言，中學文憑試如期在4月24日開考的成數非常高。教育局局長楊潤雄與考評局秘書長蘇國生今午舉行記者會，公佈文憑試將如期於4月24日開考，目標於7月22日放榜；但若開考前或其間因疫情惡化被迫暫停，未完成筆試將推遲至5月22日開考，放榜日則押後至8月；若疫情發展不容許開考，將再進一步延至6月11日開考，8月放榜，教育局會繼續審視疫情及諮詢專家意見。若疫情嚴竣令考試未能在6月11日完成開考，將取消文憑試，並根據考生校內成績及過往文憑試表現作評核。《蘋果》正直播記者會情況。"},{"pid":"cfc74236ff24ad0973a72a1c291f0de20e461182","tid":1973302,"uid":251328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:39:50.000Z","msg":"4月24日開考，等啲人焗住去，<br />\n政府：你驚傳染咪咪撚考囉！<br />\n依，有大爆發啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪到時再諗睇吓點先算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}